<h2 id="内容摘要" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#内容摘要"><span>内容摘要</span></a></h2>
<p>ReMax是一种简单、有效且高效的强化学习方法，旨在对齐大型语言模型。本文回顾了策略梯度与PPO算法的基本概念，并介绍了如何通过优势函数指导策略更新。</p>
<h2 id="策略梯度与ppo回顾" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#策略梯度与ppo回顾"><span>策略梯度与PPO回顾</span></a></h2>
<p>策略梯度方法通过奖励估计值 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>ψ</mi><mi>t</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\psi_t</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ψ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2806em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">t</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 来提供更新幅度和方向。其公式为：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>E</mi><msub><mi>π</mi><mi>θ</mi></msub></msub><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mi>T</mi></munderover><msub><mi>ψ</mi><mi>t</mi></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∇</mi><mi>θ</mi></msub><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><msub><mi>π</mi><mi>θ</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mi>t</mi></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><msub><mi>s</mi><mi>t</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g = E_{\pi_{\theta}} \left[ \sum_{t=0}^{T} \psi_t \nabla_{\theta} \log \pi_{\theta} (a_t | s_t) \right]
